data.description: Located in the exclusive and highly sought Indian Springs this 4-bedroom 3.5-bathroom home has so much to offer from soaring ceilings, a gourmet kitchen, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a fireplace, 3 car garage, a gorgeous pool, and spacious privacy fenced backyard on a large corner lot! The home is filled with natural light coming from the wall of windows and high ceilings. Made for entertaining the kitchen, living room, and dining room are an open concept that connect to the outdoor entertaining space! Perfect for hosting summer parties or simply enjoying a quiet evening by the pool. Wonderful family home! The first floor of this home features the primary suite, with a large walk-in closet and a luxurious bath, walk-in shower double vanities, an office/second bedroom, and a half bath. Upstairs is also a huge amount of space with a second living area/media room and three guest bedrooms with large closets and two bathrooms, one bedroom features a private bathroom making it a great guest suite, and the other rooms share a large jack and jill bath. BRAND NEW ROOF, beautifully landscaped, mature trees, and amazing curb appeal. Indian Springs is known for its amenities, tightly knit community, and beautiful topography. The Award-winning school district, fine dining, local shopping & entertainment places this property at the top of the list - truly a must-see! SELLER OFFERING 5,000.00 CREDIT TOWARD CLOSING COST OR INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN   -OR-    Seller will consider VA Loan Assumption for a qualified Veteran. Lender must approve the release request and release the seller their liability. HOME READY FOR IMMEDIATE MOVE IN!!!
